edu.ncsu.csc.Galant.algorithm.code.macro

Interface Function<P,R>

  • Type Parameters:
    P - The type of the parameter.
    R - The type of the result.

    public interface Function<P,R>
    Represents a simple function that can be later called with a parameter of type P to get a result of type R and that doesn't throw any checked exceptions.
